data.comment: Today's referee, Adam Ladeback, has blown to start the match.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Malmo.
In the minute 2, Malmo awarded a free kick in their own half.
Throw-in Ostersund.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Malmo.
In the minute 5, Aly Keita (Ostersund) has been given a yellow card and will be suspended from the next match.
It's getting dangerous! Free kick for Malmo close to the penalty box.
Goal! Anders Christiansen gives Malmo a 1-0 lead in Malmo.
In the minute 8, Malmo move into a more comfortable 2-0 lead. Isaac Thelin is the scorer with a header!
That's a fine assist from Anel Ahmedhodzic.
Ostersund have been awarded a corner by Adam Ladeback.
In the minute 14, Corner awarded to Ostersund.
Free kick Malmo.
Ball goes out of play for a Ostersund goal kick.
In the minute 18, Malmo have been awarded a corner by Adam Ladeback.
Ostersund awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Ostersund in their own half.
In the minute 22, Ostersund have a goal kick.
In Malmo a free kick has been awarded the home team.
At Stadion, Malmo are penalized for being offside.
In the minute 27, Free kick for Malmo in their own half.
Malmo have been awarded a penalty in Malmo...
At Stadion, Ronald Mukiibi has been yellow-carded for the away team.
In the minute 29, Anders Christiansen gives Malmo a 3-0 lead from the penalty spot.
Free kick for Malmo in their own half.
Malmo awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 32, Ostersund's Henrik Bellman has been booked in Malmo.
Eric Larsson puts the ball in the net and the home team extend their lead. The score-line now reads 4-0.
Great play from Soren Rieks to set up the goal.
In the minute 36, Free kick for Malmo in the half of Ostersund.
Adam Ladeback signals a Ostersund throw-in in Malmo's half.
Adam Ladeback waits before resuming play because Sam Mensiro for Ostersund is still down.
In the minute 42, Corner awarded to Ostersund.
Sam Mensiro returns to the field for Ostersund after picking up a slight injury.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Ostersund in their own half.
In the minute 44, Erdal Rakip for Malmo gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
Adam Ladeback awards Ostersund a goal kick.
Adam Ladeback will wait an extra 2 minutes before blowing the whistle to end the 1st half.
In the minute 45, A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Ostersund.
In Malmo, Malmo push forward quickly but are pulled up for offside.
In the minute 45, The ref's whistle signals the end of the first-half.
The second-half is underway in Malmo.
Nikolaos Dosis is on a sub for Henrik Bellman for Ostersund.
In the minute 46, The home team replace Eric Larsson with Felix Beijmo.
The home team have replaced Ola Toivonen with Adi Nalic. This is the second substitution made today by Jon Dahl Tomasson.
Malcolm Stolt is replacing Charlie Colkett for the away team.
In the minute 48, Goal kick for Ostersund at Stadion.
Malmo to take a throw-in in Ostersund territory.
Free kick Malmo.
In the minute 53, Sam Mensiro for Ostersund has been booked by Adam Ladeback and receives a first yellow card.
Adam Ladeback awards Ostersund a goal kick.
Malmo have a goal kick.
In the minute 57, Can Malmo get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Ostersund's half?
Malmo's Arnor Traustason misses with an attempt on goal.
Ball goes out of play for a Ostersund goal kick.
In the minute 59, It's a goal kick for the away team in Malmo.
Throw-in for Malmo in the half of Ostersund.
Malmo make their third substitution with Behrang Safari replacing Jonas Knudsen.
In the minute 63, Malmo awarded a free kick in their own half.
Oscar Lewicki (Malmo) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Ostersund in their own half.
In the minute 66, Free kick for Ostersund in their own half.
Corner awarded to Malmo.
Malmo are coming forward and Soren Rieks gets in a strike, it misses the target, however.
In the minute 67, Goal kick for Ostersund at Stadion.
Throw-in high up the field for Malmo in Malmo.
Oscar Lewicki is on a sub for Isaac Thelin for Malmo.
In the minute 72, Malmo have been awarded a corner by Adam Ladeback.
Adam Ladeback awards Ostersund a goal kick.
Malmo push forward at Stadion and Lasse Nielsen gets in a strike. This is blocked, however, by a determined Ostersund defence.
In the minute 75, Ostersund awarded a free kick in their own half.
In Malmo a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Can Ostersund capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Malmo's half?
In the minute 79, Malmo have a goal kick.
Free kick for Ostersund in their own half.
Ostersund's Malcolm Stolt misses with an attempt on goal.
In the minute 80, Goal kick for Malmo at Stadion.
Throw-in for Ostersund in the half of Malmo.
Free kick for Ostersund in the half of Malmo.
In the minute 83, Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Ostersund in their own half.
Ball goes out of play for a Malmo goal kick.
Francis Jno-Baptiste is replacing Blair Turgott for the away team.
In the minute 86, Malmo have been awarded a corner by Adam Ladeback.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Malmo.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Malmo in their own half.
In the minute 87, Can Ostersund get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Malmo's half?
Free kick for Malmo in their own half.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Malmo.
In Malmo Malmo attack through Lasse Nielsen. The finish is off target, however.
Ostersund have a goal kick.
2 minutes will be added to the 2nd half.
In Malmo a free kick has been awarded the away team.
Malmo drive forward at breakneck speed but are pulled up for offside.
Adam Ladeback blows to end the match. The final score is 4-0.
Alex Purver is replacing Sam Mensiro for Ostersund at Stadion.
